                <h3><span class="status-icon"></span>About this project</h3>
                <p>
                    A personal project by a psychiatrist who dives 100+ times a year. 
                    After witnessing the 2024 bleaching event firsthand, 
                    I started tracking the data.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This site translates and visualizes NOAA Coral Reef Watch 
                    and NASA satellite data for divers and researchers in Japan. 
                    It does not propose original thresholds—it presents 
                    established science with honesty about satellite-ground discrepancies.
                </p>
